01:06:02.135 --> 01:06:05.430
<i>Lincoln Hawk,
from the truckers' division.</i>

01:06:06.556 --> 01:06:09.684
Finally, five-time
arm wrestling world champion...

01:06:09.809 --> 01:06:11.436
- Yeah!
... Bull Hurley!

01:06:11.561 --> 01:06:14.731
<i>Let's hear it for Bull.</i>

01:06:14.856 --> 01:06:20.403
I drive a truck and arm wrestle. It's
what I love to do, it's what I do best.

01:06:20.529 --> 01:06:22.906
Yeah!

01:06:23.031 --> 01:06:29.122
Bull, ladies and gentlemen, trying for an
unprecedented sixth championship title.

01:06:29.248 --> 01:06:34.711
Being number one is everything.
There is no second place. Second sucks.

01:06:34.837 --> 01:06:38.465
And now, semifinalists,
will you please take the tables?

01:06:38.590 --> 01:06:43.595
This is a double elimination tournament.
Two losses and you're out.

01:06:43.720 --> 01:06:45.347
Yeah, John! Come on!

01:06:45.472 --> 01:06:50.811
All right, gentlemen. Let's start
the competition. Good luck to all of you.

01:06:50.936 --> 01:06:53.438
We have Linc Hawk
and John Grizzly competing.

01:06:53.564 --> 01:06:56.149
- Get him off my thumb.
- This'll be a tough match.

01:06:56.275 --> 01:06:58.193
Get him off my thumb.

